OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly dry this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, though it will stay rather
OL,8,Fcloudy, particularly across the east
OL,9,Fof Wales. It will turn chilly under
OL,10,Fany lengthy cloud breaks, with a few
OL,11,Ffog patches possible.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FThere will still be a lot of
OL,14,Fcloud around on Saturday with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,16,Fdrizzle developing from the south.
OL,17,FFeeling a little milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
